Welcome to TestCase!

TestCase is a light and easy to use unit-testing system for your JavaScript
code. Former versions were dependent on the Prototype library, but since version
2.0, the project is framework free.

The files structure:

doc/ - documentation directory
lib/ - thirt party software directory
src/ - the project's source code directory
test/ - the project tests
README - this file
LICENSE - the project's license


The source code had been successfully tested on the following environments

FireFox 1.5, 2, 3
IE 6, 7
Safari 3
Opera 9
Konqueror 3.5.8